This place is awesome. We do an event here at least once a year. Shannon Lambert will work with you to help you build the party of your dreams.
You can also book them to decorate a place of your choice. They bring parties to life!

originalText.text: I have know the owner for many years she has a reputation for doing things first class. So it came as no surprise to me that she would be the proprietor of such a fine establishment. I attended a repast at Lambert Treasures recently and the event space is efficient, clean, expertly managed and the staff are kind and helpful.
